title: Hand Simulator v2 3-STEAM
description:
Hand Simulator is a game in which you control your own hands. There are many different levels where you can play with spinners, plunge into the subtleties of handling weapons, milk a cow, take part in a Mexican duel with your friends, have a good time fishing, play chess or simply chat in an anonymous club.
